  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565200/extras/a7dc35d18513286bb17752cde2ddbca5.poster.avif?t=1648517808\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565200/extras/a7dc35d18513286bb17752cde2ddbca5.webm?t=1648517808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565200/extras/a7dc35d18513286bb17752cde2ddbca5.mp4?t=1648517808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Road Flash is a racing game inspired by the visuals, games and cars from the late 80s and early 90s. <br><br>A game suitable for those who love arcade games and nostalgia.<br><br>There are 5 different maps and 6 different vehicles in total.<br><br>With the points you earn, you can unlock new cars and maps.<br><br>We also added a small combination cheat so that you can pass all the levels. (Use the arrow keys)",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565200/extras/a7dc35d18513286bb17752cde2ddbca5.poster.avif?t=1648517808\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565200/extras/a7dc35d18513286bb17752cde2ddbca5.webm?t=1648517808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1565200/extras/a7dc35d18513286bb17752cde2ddbca5.mp4?t=1648517808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Road Flash is a racing game inspired by the visuals, games and cars from the late 80s and early 90s. <br><br>A game suitable for those who love arcade games and nostalgia.<br><br>There are 5 different maps and 6 different vehicles in total.<br><br>With the points you earn, you can unlock new cars and maps.<br><br>We also added a small combination cheat so that you can pass all the levels. (Use the arrow keys)",
